{"tid":1275840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（文宣）聯署要求將林鄭開除教藉","createTime":"2019-07-01T23:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T22:48:22.000Z","uid":173852,"like":162,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f1c0460c0bb963dac2fdb80fae0f3fdd474fc2c5","tid":1275840,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:45:37.000Z","msg":"1.希望各派各教會發聲明明確指出林鄭之作為並非基督徒應有既行徑，林鄭有意識地違反基督教的原則，如誠實、正義等。<br />\n<br />\n2.如有可能，希望林鄭所屬既教會取消佢既教藉，直到其人悔改為止。<br />\n<br />\n老實講，今次基督徒做左好多野，但教會似乎係依個大是大非既問題度重係畏首畏尾、兩頭落注咁，<span style=\"color: red;\">敢膽蝦同性戀同意外懷孕既弱女子，無敢同真正既不公義對抗？</span>咁憑咩指導基督徒甚至社會大眾既信仰同生活？"},{"pid":"f48d6b03371664d397fecb84f683424703945d53","tid":1275840,"uid":137209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:48:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"99314379270c82044ed153dd024267134542d3f6","tid":1275840,"uid":173852,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:50:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>夠</strong>膽蝦同性戀同意外懷孕既弱女子，<strong>唔</strong>敢同真正既不公義對抗？"},{"pid":"eeb63f3c5ae1bd9d2b69b8bbca47e4c81a446c78","tid":1275840,"uid":34816,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:50:01.000Z","msg":"絕對支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 林奠自稱係天主教徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3cc2b0a2661e28b0db1d80ddf881f64a21381f","tid":1275840,"uid":173852,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eeb63f3c5ae1bd9d2b69b8bbca47e4c81a446c78","tid":1275840,"uid":34816,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:50:01.000Z","msg":"絕對支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 林奠自稱係天主教徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T23:51:08.000Z","msg":"依度指既基督徒包括羅馬教會、東方教會及其他